-- Yuan Is Almost 50 Percent Undervalued Against Dollar, Credit Suisse Says
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-06-23T03:55:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-23/yuan-is-almost-50-percent-undervalued-against-dollar-credit-suisse-says.html

          
          
             China’s yuan is almost 50 percent
undervalued against the dollar, Credit Suisse Group AG said.  
 The Chinese currency will appreciate more than 2.7 percent
“discounted by the forward curve over the next 12 months
against the dollar,” Andrew Garthwaite, global equity
strategist, said in a note to clients.  
